# SPA fallback — any unknown path (other than actual static assets)
# renders the React shell so client-side routing can pick up
# /track, /portal/case/:token, /survey/:token, etc.
#
# NOTE: API calls are NOT forwarded from here. Cloudflare Pages
# `_redirects` with status 200 cannot rewrite to external URLs
# (like the separate Worker domain) — it silently falls back to
# the SPA and returns HTML to JSON fetches, which breaks callers.
# Instead the frontend talks to the Worker using its absolute URL
# configured via VITE_API_URL (frontend/.env.production). CORS is
# enabled on the Worker so cross-origin requests just work.
/*  /index.html  200
